-----------
TUTORIAL 08
-----------

This is an introduction to bare-metal programming on Raspberry Pi using
C language. This module creates a program that gets input from a bluetooth
module and change relevant GPIO status, based on a pre-defined command.
This sample program also explores some information that can be gathered
using mailbox interface to the VideoCode GPU.

